==早期發現==
在奧莫河的河岸，考古學家找到來自早期[[更新世|更新世]]時代到[[上新世|上新世]]時代的[[Olduwan|Olduwan]] [[原始人|原始人]][[奧莫遺骸|化石碎片]]。這些碎片是現已滅絕的[[南方古猿|南方古猿]]的一個重要發現<ref>{{cite web |last=Crandall |first=Ben |year=2007 |language=en |url=http://www.mnsu.edu/emuseum/archaeology/sites/africa/omoriver.html |title=The Omo River Valley |publisher=eMuseum @ [[明尼苏达州立大学曼卡托分校|Minnesota State University, Mankato]] |accessdate=2007-10-31 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20061210123834/http://www.mnsu.edu/emuseum/archaeology/sites/africa/omoriver.html |archivedate=2006-12-10 }}</ref>。

